<h1 id="fe-slide-filter-view">Fe Slide Filter View</h1>

<p>Hi everybody as an iOS developer like me ;]</p>

<p>I have just released my customize control in <a href="https://github.com/NghiaTranUIT/FeSlideFilter">GitHub</a>.</p>

<p>Here video as sample :</p>
<iframe allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" frameborder="0" height="615" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/KUN6bs9pl74" width="820"></iframe>

<h1 id="technical">Technical</h1>

<p>FeSlideFilter was build on top UIView. I combine UIScrollView with paging for title filter, and Mask layer technique. Here is what’s going on:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Subclass UIView</li>
  <li>Using UIScrollView with paging for title filter</li>
  <li>Using LUT filter technique for apply effect to photo</li>
  <li>Conform UIScrollViewDelegate for interactive control – slide filter by your touch.</li>
  <li>Using Layer’s mask technique for implementing two-side previewer.</li>
  <li>Provide own delegate and datasource.</li>
</ul>

